<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fun-adj">fun <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fʌn/    美 /fʌn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>给人欢乐的；有趣的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She's really fun to be with.
和她在一起真开心。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are lots of fun things for young people to do here.
这里有许多供年轻人做的有趣的事情。</p></div></div>